---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Gemini Automator Privacy Policy">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-0">
    <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-300 mb-2">Privacy Policy</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Gemini Prompt Automator</h1>
    <p class="text-white/70 mb-8">Last Updated: December 9, 2025</p>

    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-2xl space-y-6">
      <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
        The Gemini Prompt Automator extension ("we", "us", or "our") is dedicated to protecting your privacy. This
        policy explains how we handle your data.
      </p>

      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">1. Data Collection and Usage</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          We do not collect, transmit, store, or sell any personal user data to external servers. All data processed
          by this extension is stored locally on your device.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-white/80">
          <li>
            <strong class="text-white">Prompts &amp; Settings:</strong> Your prompt queue and extension settings are
            stored in your browser's local storage (<code>chrome.storage.local</code>) and are never sent to us.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong class="text-white">Page Interaction:</strong> The extension interacts with the Google Gemini website solely
            to perform the automation tasks you initiate (typing prompts, clicking buttons, downloading images). It does not
            read or transmit your chat history beyond the immediate technical needs of the automation.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">2. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          This extension automates interactions with Google Gemini. Your use of Google Gemini is subject to Google's own Terms
          of Service and Privacy Policy. We are not affiliated with Google.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">3. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          If you have questions about this policy, please contact us via the Chrome Web Store support page.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
